Package ie.gmit.sw

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Databaseable
    Interface designed to abstract common functionality from Database class, and allow it to work with the Database Proxy.
    Processable
    Interface designed to abstract common functionality from FileParser and PredictLanguage class.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DatabaseProxy
    I have decided to implement a proxy to access the database.
    FileProcessor
    FileProcessor class that processes each line in the WiliText file.
    InitialiseDatabase
    InitialiseDatabase - Middleman class that handles all the setting up of the database.
    JobProcessor
    This class processes the jobs on the inQueue which is added by the JobProducer.
    JobProducer
    This class processes the requests and adds them to the inQueue for the JobProcessor to process.
    LanguageEntry
    Supplied LanguageEntry class that is added to the db.
    LanguageRequest
    Object which is added to the inQueue.
    OutOfPlaceMetric
    Supplied OutOfPlaceMetric class that is used to get the OutOfPlaceMetric distance between the query and database maps.
    Parser
    Parser class - Used to parse any file, and add kmers to database.
    PredictLanguage
    Class that processes the query text from the client and returns a result.
    ServiceHandler
    This servlet will be deployed on the tomcat server and is used to run the application.
    UserInput
    Class that handles user input when running servlet.
    Utilities
    Utilities methods which are abstracted and implemented from both the PredictLanguage and FileParser class.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Language
    Supplied Enum class that contains all language names.
